Dialogs.Dialog: I kind of like it like this.
I think this is pretty fun.
Urgh. This is a bit embarrassing...
Eh？ Wait. This is no good！
Hey！ What do you mean by this？
I don't know how to react to this. Geez...
I have weird feeling in my chest...
Um, I guess I like it.
If I like this too much, will I be weird？
My heart won't stop pounding so hard...
Why is it？ I feel like I'm suffocating...
You want to make me mad？
Don't you understand that I hate this！？
Of course, this is no good.
I have nothing for you even if you pat me.
Are you done patting my head？
Are you making fun of me？
Do you think I'm a kid？
Don't touch me too much. Geez.
Do you like to touch Rinko's hair that much？
Do you like touching my hair？
Hehe... My hair is getting crumpled.
I allow this because it's you.
Ah, that makes me feel good.
Hehehe... I think I'm feeling good.
You are such a bad boy！
My hair is getting crumpled... Hey, idiot！
Doing that doesn't make me happy！
Why do you touch my forehead？
What's the matter？ Why do you touch my forehead？
Ouch！ You did that all of a sudden！
Huh！ Stop it~！ You make me feel nervous.
Geez！ ...You made me utter some weird sounds！
Kyaa！！ Geez... That part is sensitive...
Wait！ Why did you do that？
Ah, is this what guys like to do？
I guess you can tell that my heart is throbbing.
Ah！ Doing this makes my heart throb...
Wait！ ...If you do this again, I'll kick you！
No！ No matter how close we are, this is a no-no！
Wanna walk arm in arm？ Well, if you insist...
My arm？ ...Hehe. What shall I do？
You can hold my arm tighter.
When you do this, I don't want to stay away from you...
If you wanna get closer to me, then do it. Come on！
M-My face isn't turning red. Yours is red, too！
When we do this, we can feel each other's body temperature...
Wanna walk arm in arm？ Don't get overfamiliar with this！
My arm？ I won't let you hold it.
Wanna walk arm in arm？ Well, we'll do it sooner or later.
I'm not in the mood. We can walk arm in arm any time later, right？
Sorry. I'm not in the mood for that.
My hand？ If it's just for a short time, I can let you hold it.
Wanna hold my hand？ Fine. But you have to be gentle.
Wanna hold my hand, right？ It's okay though.
When we hold hands, it feels like we become one.
It's fine to hold hands. Rinko doesn't hate it.
Let's make our fingers entwine. ...Yes, I like this.
When we hold hands, our eyes automatically meet.
Don't touch me as you please.
My hand？ Of course, this is no good.
I'm not in the mood for this now.
We can hold hands later whenever we want, right？
The weather is too hot for us to get closer.
Isn't the weather too hot for that？
You don't care about being sweaty？
The weather is too hot to stay close to each other.
Hey. The weather is just too hot...
I'm all sweaty. Don't get too close.
The weather is so hot, yet you still want to get closer？
Even in such hot weather, you want to touch me？
I can feel your body temperature.
Wanna come closer？ It's cold, after all.
You can come closer to me.
Don't touch any weird place, okay？
Ah, did you just touch me in the dark？
Um, it's dark. My heart is throbbing.
Ah... Wait. What are you doing？
It's dark. Are you imagining something perverted？
Hey, what are you doing？ Idiot...
It's not so embarrassing if we get closer. It's dark, after all.
No one is looking at us now. Hehe. What do we do？
Wait. This is too much for a practical joke！
Do you feel my body temperature？
Wanna walk arm in arm？ ...Well, that's fine.
Although we are lovers, this is still embarrassing.
Just the arm, all right？ Don't touch other places.
This feels kind of refreshing, huh？
Is your body temperature quite high or is it just my imagination？
You want to hold hands even when I'm wearing a swimsuit？
You're quite proactive. Is it because I'm wearing a swimsuit？
Don't worry. I won't fall down.
My hand？ Fine. But I'm wearing a swimsuit. This is a little embarrassing.
Wanna hold hands？ This is more embarrassing than when I'm wearing normal clothes.
No. My hand is all sweaty now.
Stop it. We'll look like an idiot couple.
Maybe later. It's not good to do this now...
...Wait until it gets cooler than this.
Don't stare at me. It's embarrassing...
...You face says that you want to see me in a sexier swimsuit.
Are you looking at my swimsuit or my legs？
Don't stare like that. I'm not confident with my figure...
What are you looking at？ It's embarrassing.
Are you falling in love with Rinko's beautiful legs？
Don't look at me like that！
Stop staring, or I'll kick you！
Rinko's figure is not quite good though.
...Well, I think it's okay like this.
Fine. If you want to hold my arm this much...
Hey, it's always okay to walk arm in arm.
...It feels different when I'm wearing a kimono.
Do you want to get closer to Rinko when she is wearing a kimono？
I know. You don't have to make that greedy face.
I wonder how it feels when you cuddle with someone who's wearing a kimono.
A kimono... Somehow the atmosphere is nice.
...No. Can you step away a bit？
Wanna walk arm in arm？ Not now.
My hand？ If you wanna hold it, then fine.
You have to hold my hand tightly, okay？
Are you happy to hold Rinko's hand？
Don't let go of my hand. Hold it tightly.
...I won't let you hold my hand.
No. It's already good like this.
No. We don't have to hold hands, do we？
For this, let's wait until later.
I won't kick you. It's difficult when I'm wearing this.
What's wrong？ Why are you staring at my feet？
It would feel nice to walk without shoes.
...Are you looking at my shoes or my feet？
Do you have fun looking at my feet？
If Rinko trips, you have to help, okay？
...What？ Why do you keep looking downward？
What？ You have a foot fetish？
Are you concerned so much about Rinko's feet？
Why do you keep looking downward？ Geez.
Geez... You know, I'm not a kid...
...Stop it or I wouldn't want to go home.
...Just a little bit. Just like this... okay？
You really enjoy touching my hair, don't you？
...Refrain from touching me in front of people.
Hehe... We're so in love, right？
A guy's hand is this warm...
...I want to be like this forever. But... Hey...
You don't want me to go home？ ...It's fine though.
I don't want to part with you now...
No. Don't let go of my hand.
Ah... You let go of my hand.
Your hand... Rinko really likes it.
I want to stay with you longer.
Do you like touching my hair？ It's okay though...
My ear？ Um, well, I don't mind.
My arm？ Okay, okay. Here you go.
Your hand... I don't hate it.
Touching my hair like this... It's something special, right？
It's your privilege to touch my hair.
You really like touching my hair, huh？ Hehe.
My forehead？ Is there something funny about it？ Don't make fun of me...
My forehead is very warm, but I don't have a fever. You know why, right？
Are you happy？ It's okay. You can touch my forehead.
My ears are sensitive. I won't allow anyone else to touch them.
Rinko's ears are getting hot！ It's because you touched them.
It feels good to touch my ears, huh？
My arm... Holding it is fine, so don't let go.
Even if you don't hold my arm like that, I'll still stay by your side.
Rinko's arms are always waiting for you.
When you hold my hand, it feels like I'm being pulled towards you.
Rinko's hand is feeling lonely right now.
Will you hold my hand tightly？ Is it okay if we stay like this forever？
